To Do App

What Can it Do?
1. Allows User to input tasks within his/her/their to do list
2. Allows user to mark completed tasks off of his/her/their to do list
3. Presents Numbered to do list to user when requested
4. Allows user to indicate which items are most important on his/her/their to do list
5. Allows user to add due dates to his/her/their list
6. Tells user how much time exists between now and the due date
7. Provides Users with a Main Menu where they can choose which action in which they wish to engage (adding items,
marking complete items, prioritizing to do items)